Definition.WordDefinition: Teens \Teens\, n. pl. [See {Ten}.] The years of one's age having the termination -teen, beginning with thirteen and ending with nineteen; as, a girl in her teens. [1913 Webster]
teens n 1: the time of life between the ages of 12 and 20 2: all the numbers that end in -teen
